pr_title: [GSOC/WIP] Add support for Livechat screen sharing
pr_body:
### Tasks:
- [x] Add system message (request_screenshare_access) for agent
- [x] Create a setting for admin to enable/disable screen sharing
- [x] Create a setting for admin to select screen sharing provider to be used
- [x] Add UI for agent to request screen sharing
- [x] Add setting for current provider used by the server
- [x] Add ScreensharingManager
- [x] Add Cobrowse.io provider
- [x] Add agent authentication function
- [x] Add streamers for communicating from server-side to client
- [x] Add REST API endpoint (filesharing) in livechat.room
- [x] Add iframe toggle to maximize and minimize the window
- [x] Add a screen-sharing field in livechat room model
- [x] Add custom badge function in livechatRoomTypes
